casebody.data:
Sophie Rosenberg, Respondent, v. Reece M. Oberteufer, et al., Appellants. Decided March 1, 1886. Appeal from judgment entered on verdict, and from order denying motion for new trial. Blumenstiel & Hirsh, for appellants. Kurzman & Yea-man, for respondent.

Before Sedgwick, Ch. J., and Truax, J.

Opinion per Curiam. Judgment and order affirmed, with costs.
